\par \pard\plain \sa120\nowidctlpar \f5\fs22 The Filters Toolbar is used to control the icons and lines that are drawn on the map. There are three sets:{\b 
\par Blue Set
\par }This set of icons controls the display of the UN Forces and assets. The silver-backed icon on the left can be used to toggle on and off all UN Forces and Assets.
\par {\b Red Set
\par }This set of icons controls the display of the Communist Forces and assets. The red set of icons works in the same way as the blue set.{\b 
\par Miscellaneous Set
\par }The top left icon toggles the main waypoints.
\par The bottom left icon toggles the waypoints in the target zone.
\par The top right icon toggles between displaying all the route lines and just the highlighted route.
\par The bottom right icon toggles the Front Line.
